com.github.cwilper.fcrepo.store.legacy
Interface FileStore

All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<String>, PathAlgorithm, PathRegistry
All Known Implementing Classes:
FilesystemFileStore
public interface FileStore
extends Iterable<String>, PathAlgorithm, PathRegistry

Provides read/write/iterate access to a set of files organized in directories. All paths are of the form dir/subdir/filename.
